MITCHELL, Respondent, v. TURNER, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. May 8, 1894.) Action by Sidney Mitchell, Jr., against Benton Turner.

Argued before MAYHAM, P. J., and PUTNAM and HERRICK, JJ.

Judgment affirmed, with costs. Memorandum by HERRICK, J. (Not for .publication.)
